description: Rescue services have suspended a search for the night for a second man who was on the boat.
title: Fisherman dies after trawler sinks off County Wexford coast
title_page: Fisherman dies after trawler sinks off County Wexford coast - BBC News
maintext: A man in his 60s was recovered from the water and taken to University Hospital Waterford, where he was pronounced dead.
